count(
  measurementsOutletSensorSignedValue{instance="$pdu", outletId=~"[1-9]|[1-4][0-8]", sensorType="rmsCurrent"} > 0
  and
  measurementsOutletSensorSignedValue{instance="$pdu", outletId=~"[1-9]|[1-4][0-8]", sensorType="rmsCurrent"} / 
  measurementsOutletSensorMaxValue{instance="$pdu", outletId=~"[1-9]|[1-4][0-8]", sensorType="rmsCurrent"} > 0.7
)
